<h4>
    i love that show, too! offers a way to enjoy your favorite shows<br />
    with people who share your love (passion (some may say...obsession)) for the characters and storylines.
</h4>
<hr />

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Channels</h2>
        <p>
            Find a "channel" for the show(s) you love and connect with others who love it, too.
            Can't find your favorite show? Start a channel of your own and see who loves it, too.
        </p>
    </div>
   
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Viewing Parties</h2>
        <p>
            Create Viewing Party "meetups" to watch your shows with other people who share your passion.
            Make it a viewing event at your favorite restaurant or bar or even in the comfort of your own home.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Chat</h2>
        <p>
            Can't make it to a viewing party?  You can still chat live with others while watching the show.
            Can't believe your favorite character just got shot.  Chat about it.   Wonder if your favorite couple
            will get back together?  Chat with others to see their thougths.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Search</h2>
        <p>
            Search for information about your favorite shows.  What other shows was your favorite actor in? Why is your favorite show about to be canceled?  Maybe it's the ratings. Who produces the show you love?
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<br /><br /><hr />
