        <p>Registration is easy.  Just click the button below...</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="../Account/Register">Click to register &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6" align="center">
        <h2>Returning?</h2>
        <p>Already a member, then just click below to get back to business...</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="../Home/ToDo">Welcome Back! &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>


